C:\Users\kusta\Layerinfinite\Outcome>ARNING: This tool has FAILED on ${taskType} ${failPct} of the time (${sampleSize} recorded ${pluralize(sampleSize, 'outcome', 'outcomes')}).${degradingNote}Strongly consider using ${recommendedAlternative} instead — it has succeeded ${altPct} of the time for this task.`;
