**Step 3.4 — Business Webhook Endpoint** (`business-webhook.ts`)
- `POST /v1/webhook/callback` — external systems POST delayed outcomes
- Request body:
  ```json
  {
    "decision_id": "dec_...",
    "layer": 2,
    "success": false,
    "reason": "memory_leak_detected",
    "metadata": { "leak_mb": 512 }
  }
